":497054,"uid":36136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"Swype都做到？"},{"pid":"008bb91fa28acb46655b34a166a59994af8bee1d","tid":497054,"uid":71936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:27:04.000Z","msg":"如果sony keyboard 可以好似swiftkey 咁同時多語言咁用 都好想用返佢"},{"pid":"2eb947dfe7d553247edf1bd1beac5fcb703aea7e","tid":497054,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T18:05:59.000Z","msg":"其實你google就有，不過冇中文"},{"pid":"639c912be89b597561c78e0b70bcd35e11e95ab5","tid":497054,"uid":88332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩咁特別？？</blockquote><br />\n中文筆劃有得直接手寫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/211829_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F211829_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=0948992c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其中之一啦<br />\n同埋個版面簡潔d  <br />\n成個鍵盤排位都唔同<br />\nd細節位講唔到  總之轉左用Google input 兩個星期都沒慣"},{"pid":"6e778a0a56d5b365d39adf69d5f9a63bb3956f7a","tid":497054,"uid":88332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你google就有，不過冇中文</blockquote><br />\n有搵過 就係唔見有  <br />\n都係打中文多  得eng 無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c62b55734a8f49995fa50ecc4fa8215b7ca131","tid":497054,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:08:19.000Z","msg":"巴打google 粵語輸入好用喎，可能你之前太慣用sony果個姐。你用開google 果個，以後你點轉android 機都唔再有唔適應問題，好方便喎"},{"pid":"31a23bc169609e5eb0cda5a98c284530706c96bc","tid":497054,"uid":61094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T03:46:28.000Z","msg":"sony input超正，尤其起細mon機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜z3c中伏，永不錄用。前幾年得sony input有中文input+英文swipe，而google input都得。想要其他中文鍵盤直接手寫可以試下swype，但我總覺得個app疾疾地"},{"pid":"29a6d1556d21ed02f126856c50deaaffa2245b9e","tid":497054,"uid":88332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打google 粵語輸入好用喎，可能你之前太慣用sony果個姐。你用開google 果個，以後你點轉android 機都唔再有唔適應問題，好方便喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n硬係用唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講不出所以"},{"pid":"51384f7e657e7f0c82c035e8c7549ec28cecc502","tid":497054,"uid":42426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"轉左用iphone半年<br />\n用緊好多人介紹隻kaiboard<br />\n但都係鍾意sony果隻多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7061ff352915ce40b19e602e6d1b212e81b251b","tid":497054,"uid":88332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sony input超正，尤其起細mon機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜z3c中伏，永不錄用。前幾年得sony input有中文input+英文swipe，而google input都得。想要其他中文鍵盤直接手寫可以試下swype，但我總覺得個app疾疾地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其中一個重點!!<br />\n我前一部係sony z ultra 6.44吋mon<br />\n用左4年<br />\n而家用5t 嗰mon窄左唔少  但Google input d鍵反而比以前多  搞到更難上手"}]}